{"tid":270530,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"[概念圖]尖沙咀賣藝日本仔Wally","createTime":"2017-06-04T11:43:19.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-03T04:01:19.000Z","uid":69088,"like":3,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"99576cbf3675cbdfeed5bf17d80107355fe09c38","tid":270530,"uid":69088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T11:43:19.000Z","msg":"是咁的，大半年前<br />\n已見到佢係尖沙咀碼頭，彈結他唱日文歌<br />\n<br />\n概念圖<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/04/193832_545c876335936bbfa6b7fcc9f7ebb218.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F04%2F193832_545c876335936bbfa6b7fcc9f7ebb218.jpg&h=722eb860&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n然後大半年過去<br />\n依然係同一個位置、同一件衫、同一首歌⋯<br />\n<br />\n唔同嘅係<br />\n依家連係旺角都見到佢<br />\n依然係同一個位置、同一件衫、同一首歌⋯<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/04/193931_c556e5fdc7720875b4dd014584c56e8b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F04%2F193931_c556e5fdc7720875b4dd014584c56e8b.jpg&h=dcd1e3a0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有無巴絲同佢傾過，到底佢知唔知<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n依家去大阪環球影城<br />\n買唔買express pass好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/04/194028_44c807ce7e1765b70c7817b6259e3a4d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F04%2F194028_44c807ce7e1765b70c7817b6259e3a4d.jpg&h=3a4d5b19&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d1c6951d9095bf77bf02947162d454f777ef19a1","tid":270530,"uid":103380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T11:45:56.000Z","msg":"抄整moon潮文都比啲誠意啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4400ddc0f8f8cdbfe40ef82a72e4b9d799e4388f","tid":270530,"uid":21423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T11:47:10.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"88f7c3387ed98818f8704457b37f4fc479eb7ace","tid":270530,"uid":69088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T11:48:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>抄整moon潮文都比啲誠意啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n無抄<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5fd607ca1ae5db2af669e447ff3510980ab4a0b4","tid":270530,"uid":55924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T12:43:42.000Z","msg":"假日必買<br />\n平日唔買就預全日排隊先玩得哂"},{"pid":"dbee839cdd3418d9af3926e69b6d3fb6d7a6bb19","tid":270530,"uid":15440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T15:20:09.000Z","msg":"唔買，都唔多野玩"},{"pid":"6f4b339c1b7ff001004610591c8820c2f1c60827","tid":270530,"uid":56775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T15:41:36.000Z","msg":"去左荃灣"},{"pid":"76a44859199bf2fe1755d860336c4ab480398ea9","tid":270530,"uid":69088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T16:05:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>去左荃灣</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n荃灣邊度有得賣藝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n諗唔到有咩位，海濱？"},{"pid":"476b1d33e26ecb82a7476153d8066bb9f87a4513","tid":270530,"uid":59886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T16:06:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>去左荃灣</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n荃灣邊度有得賣藝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n諗唔到有咩位，海濱？</blockquote><br />\n卓悅"},{"pid":"ce8b570fdde67459290e749cff013e59b2993987","tid":270530,"uid":69088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T16:28:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>去左荃灣</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n荃灣邊度有得賣藝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n諗唔到有咩位，海濱？</blockquote><br />\n卓悅</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係咪分身<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n通常下午旺角，夜尖沙咀<br />\n仲唧到時間去荃灣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nWALLY軍團"},{"pid":"990fd567f40a3c5890df0d53205391c7dedae1ae","tid":270530,"uid":35644,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T16:43:42.000Z","msg":"有個早啲入場嘅卷（好平） 唔知早10定15分鐘入<br />\n一入到去就狗衝去你最想玩個隻game，多數都係跑去哈利波特 好多人一齊跑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n然後你玩完第1隻game就可以食住個勢衝去第2想玩嘅game（呢個時候普通票嘅人仲排緊哈利波特） 咁樣比平時排快好多<br />\n到你玩完第2隻game之後就會開始回復普通票嘅狀態 玩咩game都要排好耐<br />\n咁呢個時候就可以慢慢周圍行下 飲下butterbeer<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6cd323947d5cb3c5b4fe34de22c71a12f1ec40e9","tid":270530,"uid":58254,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T17:34:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>去左荃灣</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n荃灣邊度有得賣藝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n諗唔到有咩位，海濱？</blockquote><br />\n卓悅</blockquote><br />\n即係邊到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b71534583d71885dfde702d4815bea705032f35","tid":270530,"uid":57927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T23:01:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>去左荃灣</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n荃灣邊度有得賣藝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n諗唔到有咩位，海濱？</blockquote><br />\n卓悅</blockquote><br />\n即係邊到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n甜品街果頭"},{"pid":"890150269194805ac35de20c12222002b140f7bd","tid":270530,"uid":69088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-05T02:22:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有個早啲入場嘅卷（好平） 唔知早10定15分鐘入<br />\n一入到去就狗衝去你最想玩個隻game，多數都係跑去哈利波特 好多人一齊跑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n然後你玩完第1隻game就可以食住個勢衝去第2想玩嘅game（呢個時候普通票嘅人仲排緊哈利波特） 咁樣比平時排快好多<br />\n到你玩完第2隻game之後就會開始回復普通票嘅狀態 玩咩game都要排好耐<br />\n咁呢個時候就可以慢慢周圍行下 飲下butterbeer<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n正評俾巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bae31b81617174b0915f103d061e6974c5740519","tid":270530,"uid":53553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T04:01:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}